@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequentiediagram: Hein Hopmann Modbus TCP Interactie

box "Node.js Applicatie" #F8F9FA
    participant "HopmannAdapter" as App
    participant "net.Socket" as Socket
    participant "jsmodbus Client" as JSMB
end box

box "Netwerk" #E9ECEF
    participant "TCP/IP Stack" as Net
end box

box "Hardware" #D4EDDA
    participant "Hein Hopmann Unit\n(Modbus Server)" as HH
end box

autonumber

== Initialisatie ==
App -> Socket : new net.Socket()
App -> JSMB : new TCP(socket, unitId)
note right of JSMB: UnitID wordt hier gekoppeld aan de Client

== Verbinding Opbouwen ==
App -> Socket : socket.connect(host, port)
activate Socket
Socket -> Net : [TCP SYN]
Net -> HH : [TCP SYN]
HH -> Net : [TCP SYN, ACK]
Net -> Socket : [TCP SYN, ACK]
Socket -> App : Event: 'connect'
deactivate Socket

== Modbus Data-uitwisseling ==
group Promise: readOrWrite
    App -> JSMB : readInputRegisters(register, 1)
    activate JSMB
    JSMB -> Socket : Schrijf ADU Frame (Raw Bytes)

    note over Socket, HH: [MBAP Header] [PDU: Func 04, Reg 0x00, Count 1]

    Socket -> HH : Verstuur pakket over Ethernet
    HH -> HH : Verwerk register aanvraag
    HH -> Socket : Respons (bijv: 0x00D7 voor 21.5°C)

    Socket -> JSMB : Event: 'data'
    JSMB -> App : Resolve(out: 215)
    deactivate JSMB
end

== Verbinding Verbreken ==
App -> Socket : socket.end()
activate Socket
Socket -> HH : [TCP FIN]
HH -> Socket : [TCP ACK]
deactivate Socket
destroy Socket

note over App: Resultaat: 215 / 10 = 21.5°C
@enduml